{"tid":561941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"快速提升全體港豬對政治嘅基本認識！！","createTime":"2018-02-15T12:28:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-15T12:55:18.000Z","uid":79627,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"44c384bea5ed43651937b44a28b741e1bce6f93c","tid":561941,"uid":79627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T12:28:32.000Z","msg":"啱啱問老母立法會全體議員幾多個，竟然答我56<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對政治有認識嘅藍絲都冇呢類人咁衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係好撚可悲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n令到我諗，點先可以令港豬對政治嘅認識多啲呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每年做個簡單測驗，問每個納稅人香港政治嘅基本常識，例如立會議員任期、政制等等。<br />\n<br />\nfail 嘅話來年交3倍稅。相信不出2年，港豬數目起碼少1半"},{"pid":"2c382e34a7f96cb9a2a8af7f141a5f128703b7b0","tid":561941,"uid":4780,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T12:32:32.000Z","msg":"關我鬼事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"def6999b24932bc0da540a00c324e76a414ef91b","tid":561941,"uid":57961,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T12:34:16.000Z","msg":"然而你冇強逼成年人學習政治既權力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一係就好似免費教育咁逼學生從小學起，然而又有另一個問題：內容由邊個決定？一唔小心又變國教風波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cad760673cbf9b0604ca7a66bdc4422de0aa2d38","tid":561941,"uid":53687,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T12:36:48.000Z","msg":"教佢兩樣嘢：<br />\n1.立法會議員無權發動新議案，所以民主派只可以阻止衰議案，無權提好議案；<br />\n2.功能組別由政府操縱確保皇黨佔大多數，可以否定由議員修改後嘅議案，所以民主派無辦法改到有利普羅大眾再通過。<br />\n結論：民主派唔係唔想建設，係無權建設。"},{"pid":"2a974b0e1e8af367c5373cae199791f4c2c7150c","tid":561941,"uid":53687,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cad760673cbf9b0604ca7a66bdc4422de0aa2d38","tid":561941,"uid":53687,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T12:36:48.000Z","msg":"教佢兩樣嘢：<br />\n1.立法會議員無權發動新議